\&        DB<5>
.Ve
.PP
And if you want to repeat any previous command, use the exclamation: '\fB!\fR':
.PP
.Vb 9
\&        DB<5> !4
\&        p \*(Aqsaw \-> \*(Aq.($cnt += map { print "$_\en" } grep(/the/, sort @data))
